daffy 's rhapsody is a 2012 theatrical 3d computer-animated short film starring mel blanc as daffy duck ( via an archive recording of a song , " daffy duck 's rhapsody " , which was recorded in the 1950s by capitol records ) and billy west as elmer fudd .   it was released on february 10 , 2012 in front of journey 2 : the mysterious island .   the short has not been released on home video .   this short is currently the most recent cartoon to feature blanc in an acting role .